>> title: Sodium Caseinate
>> source: https://www.ornua.com/product/caseinates/
>> description: Caseinates are highly-functional ingredients made by solubilising acid casein with alkali.

Prepare some @acid casein{50%g}.

Dissolve @baking soda{1%tbsp} in @water{100%mL}.

Mix acid casein with the baking soda solution.

Use a #blender to create a finely dispersed mixture.

Continue until casein is dissolved, forming a grey-ish solution.
